graph TB
    subgraph "TrustyAI Service Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Reconciler]
        Controller -->|reconciles| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        TrustyAICR[TrustyAIService CR<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources (per TrustyAIService)"
        direction TB
        TrustyAIDeployment[TrustyAI Service Deployment<br/>Quarkus App]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        InternalSvc[Internal Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP, 443/TCP HTTPS]
        TLSSvc[TLS Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt]
        ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitor<br/>Prometheus]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Storage]
        SA[ServiceAccount]

        TrustyAIDeployment -.->|sidecar| OAuthProxy
        TrustyAIDeployment -->|exposed by| InternalSvc
        OAuthProxy -->|exposed by| TLSSvc
        TLSSvc -->|external access| Route
        TrustyAIDeployment -->|monitored by| ServiceMonitor
        TrustyAIDeployment -->|mounts| PVC
    end

    User[User/System] -->|creates| TrustyAICR
    TrustyAICR -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|creates/manages| TrustyAIDeployment
    Controller -->|creates| InternalSvc
    Controller -->|creates| TLSSvc
    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceMonitor
    Controller -->|creates| PVC
    Controller -->|creates| SA

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        KServe[KServe InferenceServices]
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Deployments]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        Database[External Database]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/patches| KServe
    Controller -->|patches env vars| ModelMesh
    ModelMesh -->|payload processing| TrustyAIDeployment
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAIDeployment
    TrustyAIDeployment -->|DATABASE mode| Database

    subgraph "Kubernetes Resources"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Controller -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    User -->|kubectl apply| K8sAPI

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustyAICR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustyAIDeployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Database fill:#f8e71c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
